description: The MSCI World Energy TRN Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: Large and mid-cap companies from global developed markets part of the Energy sector as classified by GICS Weighted by free-float adjusted market capitalisation Reviewed on a quarterly basis Additional information on the index, selection and weighting methodology is available at https://www.msci.com
name: Xtrackers MSCI World Energy UCITS ETF 1C
